{"tid":2439152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"突發!韓國女星李知恩被揭於家中身亡!","createTime":"2021-03-09T04:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T11:17:43.000Z","uid":237562,"like":8,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"96e41249de6653259fac686ab5288994ecc726b8","tid":2439152,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"活躍於90年代的韓國女星李知恩今日爆出死訊，被揭發於家中身亡，終年49歲。據當地媒體引述警方消息，李知恩的友人表示因為聯絡不上而報警。警方在昨晚約8時左右接報到場，發現李知恩已在家中離世。警方認為需要進行屍檢決定死因，正與其家人進行商討。有指李知恩在兒子入伍服兵役後一直獨居至今。<br />\n<br />\n李知恩於1994年以模特兒身份入行，曾演出《錦紅啊，錦紅啊》、《年輕人的陽地》等影視作品而為人認識，她更憑《錦紅啊，錦紅啊》獲頒春史電影獎、青龍獎及大鐘獎的最佳女新人獎，而2004年播出的劇集《海神》是她最後一部演藝作品。"},{"pid":"a56e233158fc85239eeb667a36c9a2dd59d69dbd","tid":2439152,"uid":236359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"圖報?"},{"pid":"61e5c9925f412c51578c1ee9c11a8b6c803536de","tid":2439152,"uid":232077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b003a8c87d5bb87a5941f5aa0c2249f041eac313","tid":2439152,"uid":322685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6604bae5e5b89d243bf41a8b4b379d18cfb45ad6","tid":2439152,"uid":358542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a56e233158fc85239eeb667a36c9a2dd59d69dbd","tid":2439152,"uid":236359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"圖報?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"快到咁"},{"pid":"8eb0a1c02f1d6121a88b2b46b73dd6411f362a18","tid":2439152,"uid":87172,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"李知恩，藝名IU，韓國創作歌手、女演員。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f379f9cd13c648bcca075287872577c297b7e9a9","tid":243